Section 5.4 . The Corporation shall be precluded from asserting in any judicial proceeding commenced pursuant to this that the procedures and presumptions of this Agreement are not valid, binding and enforceable and shall stipulate in any such court that the Corporation is bound by all the provisions of this Agreement.
